<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.7.9">
<l>puḷḷiṉvāy piḷantāy marutiṭai pōyiṉā yerutē ḻaṭarttaveṉ</l>
<l>kaḷḷa māyavaṉē karumāṇikkac cuṭarē</l>
<l>teḷḷiyār tirunāṉ maṟaikaḷ vallār malitaṇ cirīvara maṅkai</l>
<l>uḷḷirunta ventā yaruḷā yuyyumā ṟeṉakkē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>You who tore the mouth of the bird, you who went in between the myrobalan trees, my deceptive</l>
<l>trickster who killed the seven bulls, glow of black ruby,</l>
<l>my father who sits in cool Cirīvaramaṅkai where abound those lucid people who master</l>
<l>the four holy Vedas, grace me with way to escape.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
